                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "Subjugation: Koukou Sendou"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">Summon</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">End Phase</span>: Deal 1 <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 172, 255)\">Electro DMG</span>, applies <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Crowfeather Cover</span> to friendly active character.</p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Usage(s): 1</span></p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(236, 229, 216)\">Crowfeather Cover</span></strong></p><p>The character with this attached deals +1 <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Elemental Skill </span>and <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Elemental Burst </span>DMG.</p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Usages: 2</span></p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/02/25/35428890/db13288db6b90ec33f8adc2656d2019f_3869125360313337535.png",
                "id": "talent448",
                "key": "Tengu Juurai: Ambush",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 0,
                    "point_type": ""
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/02/26/35428890/1ce18b0d1d4b2b162276892a85feea79_6669147345964216318.png",
                "title": "Tengu Juurai: Ambush"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">Summon</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">End Phase</span>: Deal 2 <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 172, 255)\">Electro DMG</span>, applies <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Crowfeather Cover</span> to friendly active character.</p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Usage(s): 2</span></p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(236, 229, 216)\">Crowfeather Cover</span></strong></p><p>The character with this attached deals +1 <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Elemental Skill </span>and <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Elemental Burst </span>DMG.</p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Usages: 2</span></p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/02/25/35428890/db13288db6b90ec33f8adc2656d2019f_8797410025754411995.png",
                "id": "talent2558",
                "key": "Tengu Juurai: Stormcluster",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 0,
                    "point_type": ""
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/02/26/35428890/7a1026e18244fc72af3873f6a6dc44ab_5461997373141393619.png",
                "title": "Tengu Juurai: Stormcluster"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p>Applies Electro and can trigger the following Elemental Reactions:</p><p>[<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 172, 255)\">Electro </span>+ <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 153)\">Pyro</span>] <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Overloaded</span>: DMG +2 for this instance, the target is forcibly switched to the next character</p><p>[<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 172, 255)\">Electro </span>+ <span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 255)\">Cryo</span>] <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Superconduct</span>: DMG +1 for this instance, deal 1 Piercing DMG to all opposing characters except the target</p><p>[<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 172, 255)\">Electro </span>+ <span style=\"color: rgb(128, 192, 255)\">Hydro</span>] <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Electro-Charged</span>: DMG +1 for this instance, deal 1 Piercing DMG to all opposing characters except the target</p><p>[<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 172, 255)\">Electro </span>+ <span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 136)\">Dendro</span>] <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Quicken</span>: DMG +1 for this instance, creates a [<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Catalyzing Field</span>] that grants +1 DMG to the next 2 instances of Dendro or Electro DMG</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/02/25/35428890/11ea6117480145a30b7893f1e8bd7115_6391055713841955300.png",
                "id": "talent69396",
                "key": "Electro DMG",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 0,
                    "point_type": ""
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "Electro DMG"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(236, 229, 216)\">Physical DMG</span></strong></p><p>Physical DMG will not apply any Elements, nor can it engage in Elemental Reactions.</p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(236, 229, 216)\">Usage(s)</span></strong></p><p>After this card's effect is triggered, 1 <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Usage </span>of it will be consumed.</p><p>This card will be discarded immediately once it has 0 <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Usages </span>remaining.</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/02/25/35428890/1ece3cf73687b4b134d3d9027b718b40_4834324059977428747.png",
